BreastInClass-AsianFlatChest

Get better version on my BMAC page.

Some people just don’t like big breasts…

We love small breasts, flat chest.

This is the Lora that I have been using all the time. Now I share it for you to generate small breast, flat chest.

Support me on my patreon, help me upgrade Hardware for trainning and testing more models. Or just buy me a coffee. thanks~

What it is

This is a LORA that use in text2img to get small breast, flat chest images.

How to control

You can control Lora weight and use keywords: "flatchest"

Set higher weights of keywords, it will work!

What may happen

When your Lora weight is so high, it may let you doll become thinner(it's an extra surprise),

you may see bone lines, burst tendons, blue veins, blood vessels, skin wrinkles…, so you can put these in negative prompts as well.

Tips:

  • Lora weights 0.2~0.9

  • Use keyword "flatchest", set this keywordweight up to 1.4, you will love it.

  • Very high weights may cause thinner(it's an extra surprise), may see bone lines, burst tendons, blue veins, blood vessels, skin wrinkles, use negative prompts as well.
